SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: ModuleID
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: ID of the module to which the table belongs.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Type
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Type of module. "M" for normal module, "T" for template module or "P" for package module. If not given, use "M".

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: canBeNull
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: "true" or "false" to indicate if the column can be nullable or not.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: HelpComment
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Help comment.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: JavaClass
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Java Class name for the auto-generated class for the ORM, to manage the table records. Only the class name.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: TabLevel
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Level of the tab, can be 0 for the header or 1,2,3 for tabs and subtabs.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Description
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Description of the module.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: moduleID
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: ID of the module to which the column belongs.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: name
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Name of the column in the AD. This name is used to generate the property of the auto-generated Java class and to display it in the system. It can be prefixed or modified under certain conditions. If modified, it will be reported in the response.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: referenceID
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Reference ID for the column. If the ID is for Table or TableDir, it may be changed automatically if conditions require it.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Version
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Version of the module, if not given, set 1.0.0.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Name
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Search term.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: DataAccessLevel
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: If the user does not specify one, use "3" as the default value

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Description
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Useful short Description.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: ModuleName
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Descriptive name of the module.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: QuerySelect
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Query of the view.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: columnNameDB
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Name of the column in the database, prefixes can be added under certain conditions, if modified, they will be informed in the response.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: tableID
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: The ID of the table where the column will be added.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Mode
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Mode to use the webhook. Can be "READ_ELEMENTS" or "WRITE_ELEMENTS"

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: TableID
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: If specified, validates only this table. Otherwise, all tables are validated.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: DBPrefix
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: DB Prefix of the module where the tab belongs

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: HelpComment
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Help comment to indicate to the user how to use the column.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: KeyWord
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Mode to search. Can be TAB, TABLE or WINDOW

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: WindowID
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Record ID of the window where the tab belongs

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: DBTableName
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Name of the Table/View in the Database.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: JavaPackage
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Java package of the classes generated in the module.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Name
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Name of the window.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: WindowTabID
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Record ID of the tab.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Name
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Descriptive Name of the Table

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: ModuleLicense
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Licence of distribution. If not given, set "Apache License 2.0". Available values are ["Apache License 2.0", "Openbravo Public License", "Mozilla Public License 1.1", "Etendo Commercial License"]

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Name
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: DB view name, without the DB Prefix. by convention the views have a "_v" and the end of the name.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: TableName
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: DB Table name of the Table linked to the tab.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: TableName
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Tablename of the table.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: DBPrefix
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Prefix of the DB elements that the module will contain.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: Prefix
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: DB prefix of the module.

SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.NAME: defaultValue
SMFWHE_DEFINEDWEBHOOK_PARAM.DESCRIPTION: Default Value for the Column. If the Column cannot be null, this value is mandatory.
